div.div: Commented on #6 [Eclipse] Phase 3 - Consolidation of Automation Workflows (Final)

New problem has been identified: In some cases, it is possible that the MAL anime and manga feeds will fail because of missing/null information provided by the API. The existing code will have to be modified in order to handle such cases. This problem has already been fixed in the latest commits: https://github.com/LuminisNobilite/Eclipse/commit/70d9d682c85f8709096a314ceef3cfa840296f77 https://github.com/LuminisNobilite/Eclipse/commit/22995a94054d139964b218d2404ac18abeb9fcd1

Update _Guilded__MyAnimeList_Feed___Reisonancia_Manga__Luminis_Nobilite_.json
Fixed issues when missing or null data was present in any of the embed fields.

Update _Guilded__MyAnimeList_Feed___Reisonancia_Anime__Luminis_Nobilite_.json
Fixed issues when missing or null data was present in any of the embed fields.
